{"tid":865554,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"(大結局)粉俠傳伝CASE 145 粉俠伝","createTime":"2018-10-17T07:15:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T18:57:49.000Z","uid":39181,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a779bc94ab2555cedc03cca5458c3374f946a39a","tid":865554,"uid":39181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T07:15:33.000Z","msg":"袁生似乎冇係連登分享，連載左8年既粉俠傳要大結局了，同時亦係畫左成廿年既袁生三部曲既終結，由五星陣、神龍刺青、粉俠傳仲有格劍，一直陪住大家係香港網絡世界長大<br />\n<br />\n雖然大家有時會笑下袁生，但其實大家都好佩服佢既毅力，就算工作幾忙、被人恥笑、人生有幾多不如意，都會風雨不改咁畫漫畫，而佢既作品啟發都大家進行二創，仲成功咁聚集一班鍾意畫畫既網民<br />\n<br />\n袁生簡直係香港次文化既代表人物之一，雖然香港好多野都變差但好慶幸既係我地仲有袁生，感謝袁生一路而舨既付出，依家我地一齊睇下粉俠傳既大結局<br />\n<br />\n利申:唔係袁生分身<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/11/Fmp1lu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F11%2FFmp1lu.jpg&h=958b0a4a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/04/XvQ4Fn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F04%2FXvQ4Fn.jpg&h=6c89568f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/11/g9eatP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F11%2Fg9eatP.jpg&h=04259bd3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/11/zv85PO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F11%2Fzv85PO.jpg&h=ccaa33cf&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/11/coDueU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F11%2FcoDueU.jpg&h=8dd6277a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/11/gaXWlm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F11%2FgaXWlm.jpg&h=b191e580&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/11/vR3Nkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2